# ChangeLog for clip-layout/baselayout-core-user

*baselayout-core-user-1.1.0 (07 Mar 2016)

  07 Mar 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.1.0.ebuild, -baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r5.ebuild:
  Create lib64 on clip 64 bits.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r5 (17 Dec 2008)

  17 Dec 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r5.ebuild, -baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r4.ebuild:
  Add /mnt/cdrom.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r4 (11 Apr 2008)

  11 Apr 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r4.ebuild, -baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r3.ebuild:
  Add /mnt/usb.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r3 (05 Dec 2007)

  05 Dec 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r3.ebuild, 
  -baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add /etc/gre.d symlink for acroread.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r2 (15 Nov 2007)

  15 Nov 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add IUSE clip-deps to remove dependency on baselayout-clip.

  07 Nov 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  Remove all ebuilds before 1.0.3-r1.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r1 (16 Jul 2007)

  16 Jul 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Create etc tree with views.eclass.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.3 (17 Jan 2007)

  17 Jan 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.3.ebuild:
  Add clip-single support : no point creating /xauth and /viewers in that
  case.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.2 (09 Nov 2006)

  09 Nov 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Add /etc/core support, so that we can use /user without mounting
  the whole /etc to it. baselayout-clip dependency bumped to 1.3.4, 
  accordingly.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0.1 (03 Nov 2006)

  03 Nov 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Add /var/run/authdir mountpoint.

*baselayout-core-user-1.0 (19 Sep 2006)

  19 Sep 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-user-1.0.ebuild:
  Initial import. Skeleton tree for the newborn CLIP user view. 
